      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i got prescribed antibiotics for this skin infection i had a few days ago. the doctor gave me a 10 day supply but i've been taking them for 3 days and the redness and swelling are basically gone. i feel totally fine now. do i really need to finish the whole 10 days or can i just stop since the infection seems to be gone? i dont really like taking all these chemicals if i dont have to",
