    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds pretty intense... \"killing me\"? i mean i know bacteria is bad but i feel so much better today. it just feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine for a problem that's already solved. are you sure it's actually dangerous to stop? i've heard people do it all the time when they stop feeling sick.",
